# Tailwind CSS Boilerplate

### start
```
git clone repository
cd directory
npm install
npm run dev


# Very begining to build tailwindcss
  - create index.html in empty directory
  - create tailwind.css file in in css directory 
  # package initilization
    - npm init -y

  # install npm dependences
    - npm install tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer vite
    - In here vite is auto watch server build in tailwindcss when css anything

  # create postcss and tailwindss config file
    - npx tailwindcss init -p